{"tid":1661834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［區選］長毛梁國雄入閘成功對戰李慧琼","createTime":"2019-10-18T11:06:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T12:20:38.000Z","uid":22556,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"8de5e67098642b324bd6a8e3f093b9d4ca7e2b93","tid":1661834,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T11:06:22.000Z","msg":"【即時；提名有效】本會2019區議會選舉九龍城土瓜灣北選區候選人梁國雄（長毛），被通知提名有效。<br />\n----------------------------------------<br />\n社民連義工招募：<a href=\"https://forms.gle/k4S25duc3wdHjRJw5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2Fk4S25duc3wdHjRJw5&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz%2Fno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=0870b119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/k4S25duc3wdHjRJw5</a><br />\n#決戰李慧琼<br />\n#光復土北<br />\n#選舉廣告<br />\n選舉廣告︳2019年10月18日〡1份〡自行製作"},{"pid":"fe9ced213919c432f78502204bd6a6445cd63bbd","tid":1661834,"uid":249263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T11:08:21.000Z","msg":"Twitter係每日必做的任務<br />\n禁兩個制都懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快啲同我retweet哂去！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日國際新聞關香港或者抵制中國事的有：<br />\nDior (向中國道歉，承認台灣係中國）<br />\n<br />\nBlizzard(共雪禁左美國大學隊賽半年，原因係美國大學隊支持Free Hong Kong)<br />\n<br />\nDreamwork（動畫畫九段線，畫出大部分的南海係屬於中國，菲律賓嚴重抗議，荷蘭海牙仲裁已經響2016裁定九段線違反聯合國國際公約，所以Dreamwork 奶共奶到洗緊細路腦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\nnba (Lebron James 鬧Morey咩都唔知就亂tweet，大家可以提出任何人都唔應該響普世價值上助紂為虐、自我審查！）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你響twitter大海中唔知retweet咩好<br />\ntwitter 組整左個bot<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz%2Fno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=03cf1c21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=